original_title: 運動部の合宿に引率で来た新婚のみずき先生は体育会系男子の凄まじいセックスに完堕ちしました。
overview: The table tennis club, which ended in disappointing results in the tournament, held a training camp for 3 nights and 4 days to strengthen their physical strength. Even after finishing hard training, the students who have a lot of physical strength are curious about the body of Mizuki Inoue, the deputy adviser. During the training camp, Mizuki had no choice but to continue to accept the students' unfaithful sex every night.
title: Newlywed Mizuki-sensei is led to the athletic club’s training camp and is completely consumed by tremendous sex… Hikari Ninomiya
